# amwurst: WURST shaped adiabatic off-resonance spin lock pulse
# H. Desvaux et al, J.Magn.Reson., 113A, 47 (1995).
# The RF field strength is calculated according to the desired
# spin-lock tilt angle and the offset frequency
%
#       Shape Parameters
#       ----------------
amf 	= wr	(amplitude modulation function)
fla 	= 35.5t	(spin lock tilt angle)
pwbw 	= 1.0	(dummy pulsewidth to bandwidth product, not used)
c1      = 40.0  (power index, n)
dash    = c1    (dash parameter)
steps 	= 200	(default number of steps)

